                        <interp inst="t18780114-195-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUIILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He also</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to a conviction of felony in January</hi>, 1876, <hi rend="italic">
at Clerken<lb></lb>well—<rs id="t18780114-195-punishment-45" type="punishmentDescription">
